Help for VHOST:

VHOST allows operators to set a virtual host on an
account. This vhost will be set on the user
immediately and each time they connect. If no vhost
is specified, clear any existing vhost.

Syntax: VHOST <nickname> [<vhost>]

Examples:
    /msg &nick& VHOST spb may.explode.on.impact
    /msg &nick& VHOST nenolod
